  "intro": "In today’s world of social media and visual storytelling, events are no longer just about food, music, and décor — they’re about unforgettable moments that people want to share.",
  "contentHtml": "<div class=\"entry-content alignfull wp-block-post-content has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-d89aad35 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-549b0c86 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-global-padding is-content-justification-left is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-column-is-layout-c4d06299 wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-body-font-family\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.453rem, 1.453rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 1.578), 2.4rem);line-height:1.1\">Why GlamBot is the<br><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#5aba47\" class=\"has-inline-color\"><strong>Ultimate Showstopper for Your Next Event</strong></mark></h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-width wp-block-button__width-100\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://one360.com.au/book/\">Hire GlamBot Today</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-119bc444 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\">\n<p class=\"has-body-font-family\" style=\"font-size:clamp(1.039rem, 1.039rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.935), 1.6rem);line-height:1.2\"><em>In today’s world of social media and visual storytelling, events are no longer just about food, music, and décor — they’re about unforgettable moments that people want to share.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-87beb0d0 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-container-content-9cfa9a5a\">Enter the <strong><a href=\"https://one360.com.au/glambot-hire/\">GlamBot</a></strong>, the high-speed robotic camera that’s taking events to the next level and leaving guests in awe. Designed to capture cinematic slow-motion footage of people in action.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p><em>Whether you’re hosting a corporate gala, wedding, awards night, or product launch, a GlamBot can instantly elevate the atmosphere and give your guests the celebrity treatment.</em></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax has-aspect-ratio wp-duotone-unset-6\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;min-height:100vh;aspect-ratio:16/9;min-height:unset;\"><div role=\"img\" aria-label=\"ONEGlam GlamBot Hire Sydney\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-833 has-parallax\" style=\"background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https://one360.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ONEGlam-GlamBot-Hire-Sydney.avif)\"></div><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-contrast-background-color has-background-dim-10 has-background-dim\"></span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-cover-is-layout-74935142 wp-block-cover-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"></p>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-2-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-6bdb84490d6f17343fceb17116e38ad3 has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-d89aad35 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"background-color:#000000;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-549b0c86 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-global-padding is-content-justification-left is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-column-is-layout-c4d06299 wp-block-column-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\">\n<p class=\"has-body-font-family has-x-large-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.1\">Why<mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#5aba47\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> <strong>GlamBot</strong></mark> is a Game-Changer for Events?</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-119bc444 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:60%\">\n<p class=\"has-body-font-family\" style=\"font-size:clamp(0.929rem, 0.929rem + ((1vw - 0.2rem) * 0.785), 1.4rem);line-height:1.2\"><em>Here’s how a <a href=\"https://one360.com.au/glambot-hire/\">GlamBot</a> can completely transform your next event experience:</em></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-87beb0d0 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-container-content-9cfa9a5a\">1. <strong>Creates Buzz and Excitement</strong><br>The presence of a <a href=\"https://one360.com.au/glambot-hire/\">GlamBot</a> instantly grabs attention. People are naturally drawn to the sleek robotic arm, and it becomes an interactive attraction in itself. It sets the tone that your event is modern, fun, and memorable.<br><br>2. <strong>Shareable Social Media Content</strong><br>In the age of Instagram, TikTok, and Reels, guests are always looking for something unique to post. GlamBot videos offer that wow-factor, encouraging attendees to tag your event and amplify your brand’s reach.<br><br><strong>3. Gives Guests the VIP Experience</strong><br>Nothing says red-carpet glamour like a personalised GlamBot moment. Your guests will feel like celebrities as they step in front of the camera — making their experience feel exclusive and luxurious.<br><br><strong>4. Customisable Branding Opportunities</strong><br>You can easily incorporate your logo, brand colours, event theme, or messaging into the final GlamBot videos. This makes it an excellent branding tool for corporate events, brand activations, and product launches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>5. <strong>Memories That Last</strong></strong><br>Beyond entertainment, GlamBots capture memories in a unique way. Guests get to take home a high-quality, professionally filmed moment that they’ll remember long after the event is over.</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:65px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-base-2-color has-contrast-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-d966662c1d813e4872c3a4d2c425e589 has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-669513ed wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:40%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-base-2-color has-text-color has-link-color has-body-font-family